      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical R2023 R1 is validated under ISO 9001-compliant QMS; FDA FEA solver operates under 21 CFR Part 820 software controls. Version-controlled input decks stored in Git with audit trail.",
      "rationale": "All three modeling environments (FDA in-house, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented quality management systems with version control and change management. Software verification records available for each solver version used. Achieved level meets required level for Medium model risk."
